extends ../commun/master-template.pug 

block content
  //- Start bloc content
  div.w3-container(style='padding:32px')
    h2 What is W3.CSS?
    ul.entries
    p W3.CSS is a modern CSS framework with built-in responsiveness:
    ul.w3-leftbar.w3-theme-border(style='list-style:none')
      li Smaller and faster than other CSS frameworks.
      li Easier to learn, and easier to use than other CSS frameworks.
      li Uses standard CSS only (No jQuery or JavaScript library).
      li Speeds up mobile HTML apps.
      li Provides CSS equality for all devices. PC, laptop, tablet, and mobile:
    br
    img(src='img_responsive.png' style='width:100%' alt='Responsive')
    hr
    h2 W3.CSS is Free
    p W3.CSS is free to use. No license is necessary.
    hr
    h2 Easy to Use
    .w3-container.w3-sand.w3-leftbar
      p
        i Make it as simple as possible, but not simpler.
        br
        | Albert Einstein
    hr
    h2 W3.CSS Web Site Templates
    p We have created some responsive W3CSS templates for you to use.
    p You are free to modify, save, share, use or do whatever you want with them:
    .w3-panel.w3-light-grey.w3-padding-16.w3-card
      h3.w3-center Band Template
      .w3-content(style='max-width:800px')
        a(href='tryw3css_templates_band.htm' target='_blank' title='Band Demo')
          img(src='img_temp_band.jpg' style='width:98%;margin:20px 0' alt='Band Template')
        br
        .w3-row
          .w3-col.m6
            a.w3-button.w3-padding-large.w3-dark-grey(href='tryw3css_templates_band.htm' target='_blank' style='width:98.5%') Demo
          .w3-col.m6
            a.w3-button.w3-padding-large.w3-dark-grey(href='w3css_templates.asp' style='width:98.5%') More Templates &raquo;
    .w3-container.w3-padding-16.w3-card(style='background-color:#eee')
      h3.w3-center Blog Template
      .w3-content(style='max-width:800px')
        img(src='img_temp_blog.jpg' style='width:98%;margin:20px 0' alt='Blog Template')
        br
        .w3-row
          .w3-col.m6
            a.w3-button.w3-padding-large.w3-dark-grey(href='tryw3css_templates_blog.htm' target='_blank' style='width:98.5%') Demo
          .w3-col.m6
            a.w3-button.w3-padding-large.w3-dark-grey(href='w3css_templates.asp' style='width:98.5%') More Templates &raquo;
  //- End bloc content